      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to share this absolute gem with you. Honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape that it still feels like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve truly babied this car since day one, and it looks practically brand new inside and out. If you\u2019ve been looking for a ride that\u2019s as close to perfect as you can get, this is the one. You\u2019ve got to see it in person to believe it\u2014come take a look!",
