    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. This example is mechanically superlative, having received proactive rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive subframe reinforcement. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, channeling power through a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis retains its original rigidity, complemented by pristine Style 67 forged wheels and factory-spec damping. Finished in Titanium Silver over a flawless Black Nappa leather interior, this vehicle is free of paint imperfections or interior wear. A turn-key specimen for the purist seeking peak atmospheric performance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
