      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve kept it in pristine shape, so it\u2019s sparkling inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for that 'brand new' feel without the brand new price tag, this is the one for you. Drop me a message\u2014I'd love to show it to you! \ud83d\ude0a",
